    <item>
      <title>管理关税贸易风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-03/managing-tariff-trade-risk-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[凯特·伯克（Kate Burke）将于7月接任Allspring Global Investments的首席执行官。她加入了彭博公开赛的兴趣，谈论她告诉投资者作为特朗普关税的股票市场卷轴。 Allspring是一家全球资产管理公司，其资产为6050亿美元。 （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-03/managing-tariff-trade-risk-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 15:10:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国和法国推动更积极的关税回应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/germany-and-france-push-for-a-more-aggressive-tariff-response</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国和德国正在推动对美国总统唐纳德·特朗普的关税措施做出更强有力的反应，并提倡有力的报复，这可以加强欧盟的谈判立场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/germany-and-france-push-for-a-more-aggressive-tariff-response</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 10:52:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的关税威胁着全球经济，商品遭受重创</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/commodities-hit-as-trump-s-tariffs-threaten-demand-and-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于唐纳德·特朗普总统对猛烈抨击的猛烈抨击，石油从工业金属到谷物的其他商品跌至谷物，这造成了一场贸易战，威胁着损害全球经济和对原材料的需求。黄金从新鲜的纪录中落下。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/commodities-hit-as-trump-s-tariffs-threaten-demand-and-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 08:57:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>丹麦股票随着关税的关税而滑入熊市市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/denmark-stock-index-set-for-bear-market-as-tariffs-novo-weigh-m91178mq</link>
      <description><![CDATA[丹麦的基准股票指数比9月份的高点下降了21％，这使其成为第一个进入熊市的主要欧洲指数，因为与关税相关的风险和Novo Novo Nordisk A/S的体重下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/denmark-stock-index-set-for-bear-market-as-tariffs-novo-weigh-m91178mq</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 07:25:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着债券的集会，股票途径加深关税冲击：市场包装</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的关税战争的影响周四遍布全球市场，击落股票并促进了进入固定收益避风港的飞行。美国股票和美元对猜测最糟糕的卖出总统的贸易攻势将阻碍美国经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 23:34:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当特朗普的关税达到价格大权时，汽车制造商闲置的植物，重新考虑价格</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/trump-spares-automakers-from-more-pain-in-reciprocal-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[生效仅几个小时后，唐纳德·特朗普总统对进口汽车的25％关税已经在全球回荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/trump-spares-automakers-from-more-pain-in-reciprocal-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 22:09:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>BC在四年内获得第四个学分降级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/british-columbia-gets-fourth-credit-downgrade-in-four-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[不列颠哥伦比亚省的信用等级已被S＆amp; p全球评级降低到A+，因为在政府支出不断提高的同时，加拿大省的经济增长降低了移民和贸易不确定性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/british-columbia-gets-fourth-credit-downgrade-in-four-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 21:03:07 GMT</pubDate>
